### 创建班级
POST http://localhost:8080/classrooms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Class Demo 20",
  "teacherUsername": "teacher_demo_20"
}

### 查看班主任的班级
GET http://localhost:8080/classrooms/teacher/teacher_demo_20

### 学生1加入班级
POST http://localhost:8080/classrooms/1/join
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentUsername": "student_demo_20"
}

### 学生2加入班级
POST http://localhost:8080/classrooms/1/join
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentUsername": "student_demo_21"
}

### 查看班级学生
GET http://localhost:8080/classrooms/1/students

### 班主任添加任课老师
POST http://localhost:8080/classrooms/1/teachers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "homeroomTeacherUsername": "teacher_demo_20",
  "teacherUsername": "teacher_demo_21"
}

### 查看班级老师
GET http://localhost:8080/classrooms/1/teachers

### 班主任移出学生
POST http://localhost:8080/classrooms/1/remove-student
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "homeroomTeacherUsername": "teacher_demo_20",
  "studentUsername": "student_demo_20"
}

### 再次查看班级学生
GET http://localhost:8080/classrooms/1/students

### 学生查看自己的提交记录
GET http://localhost:8080/student/submissions?studentUsername=xsn

### 学生查看某次提交详情
GET http://localhost:8080/student/submissions/1

### 查看本班学生提交状态
GET http://localhost:8080/teacher/assignments/1/submission-status?teacherUsername=teacher_demo_20

### 家长查看孩子学习概览
GET http://localhost:8080/parent/students/xsn/summary
